msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/name"
msgid "Battle of Hurtgen Forest [SKIRMISH]"
msgstr "Batalla del Bosque de Hurtgen [ESCARAMUZA]"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/name_big"
msgid "Battle of Hurtgen Forest"
msgstr "Batalla del Bosque de Hurtgen"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/story"
msgid "Operation Queen, Hurtgen offensive - The attack by the 28th Division started on 2nd November.\n\n2nd Rangers listen up! The forest ahead needs to be cleared of enemies. Clear the forest and chase the enemy out!\n\nGoals:\n - Clear the forest.\n - Chase the enemy from his trenches."
msgstr ""
"Operación Queen, ofensiva Hurtgen#El ataque de la 28ª División comenzó el 2 "
"de noviembre\n"
"\n"
" ¡2º Rangers escuchen!\n"
"\n"
"El bosque que tenemos delante está plagado de enemigos.\n"
"\n"
" ¡Despejad el bosque y expulsadlos!\n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
"Objetivos:\n"
"\n"
" - Despejar el bosque.\n"
"\n"
" - Expulsar al enemigo de sus trincheras."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/place"
msgid "Hurtgen Forest"
msgstr "Bosque de Hurtgen"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/date"
msgid "November, 1944"
msgstr "Noviembre, 1944"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/outro_start"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Well done! High command will be pleased. Now, it's on to the Rgine river."
msgstr ""
"¡Bien hecho! El Alto Mando estará contento. Ahora, dirijámonos al río Rgine."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"That was brutal. But you're going to bounce back! Go back, and remember you "
"might benefit from using different tactics."
msgstr ""
"Ha sido una masacre. ¡Pero te vas a recuperar! Vuelve, y recuerda que hay "
"muchas formas de alcanzar la victoria."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/outro_failed_hq"
msgid "We lost our HQ and are no longer in control here."
msgstr "Hemos perdido nuestro cuartel general y el control de la zona."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/mission_hq"
msgid "You must hold your field HQ!"
msgstr "¡Debes defender tu cuartel general!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/mission_attack"
msgid "Punch a hole in the enemy positions!"
msgstr "¡Ábrete paso entre las tropas enemigas!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/flag_capture_status"
msgid "Your soldiers secured %1%/7 German positions!"
msgstr "¡Tus soldados aseguraron %1%/7 posiciones alemanas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/narrator_start0"
msgid ""
"Welcome to the infamous Hürtgen forest! This is your field HQ, it must "
"remain in our control!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenidos al infame bosque de Hürtgen! Este es su cuartel general en "
"campo, ¡debe permanecer bajo nuestro control!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/narrator_start1"
msgid ""
"Lieutenant, we're against the ropes here, and high command deems it best to "
"seize the initiative immediately. Attack!"
msgstr ""
"Teniente, estamos contra las cuerdas, y el alto mando considera que es mejor "
"tomar la iniciativa inmediatamente. ¡Al ataque!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/narrator_start2"
msgid ""
"The germans are unprepared for a massive assault, but their fortifications "
"and obstacles will be tough to crack!"
msgstr ""
"Los alemanes no están preparados para un asalto masivo, ¡pero sus defensas y "
"fortificaciones serán duras de roer!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/narrator_start3"
msgid "Commence the assault, more reinforcements will be sent here soon!"
msgstr "¡Comiencen el asalto, pronto llegarán más refuerzos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/allied_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Attention! Our Field HQ is under threat!"
msgstr "¡Atención! ¡Nuestro cuartel general está siendo atacado!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/allied_enemy_plane"
msgid "Enemy plane!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡Avión enemigo!!!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/allied_enemy_plane2"
msgid "German aircraft inbound!"
msgstr "¡Llegan aviones alemanes!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/player_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Hold the command post or go down trying! We cannot afford to retreat!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mantened el puesto de mando o morid en el intento! ¡No podemos permitirnos "
"retroceder!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_10_skirmish_hurtgen_forest/hq_bonus"
msgid "Attention! Now you can request an airstrike."
msgstr "¡Atención! Ahora puede solicitar un ataque aéreo."
